; Stellogen Prelude
; Common macros for type system and testing

; Macro for type assertion (iterates over galaxy of tests).
; The expansion carries the § marker: every call site becomes a
; check-phase item, evaluated by 'sgen check' and skipped by 'sgen run'.
(macro (:: Tested Test)
  §(forall Test T
    (== @(exec @#Tested #T) ok)))
